{"tid":2436702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"自稱滿族紅三代「不想孩子活在控制下」 「中國天才」潛日 復出反共","createTime":"2021-03-07T10:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T10:46:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"65f372bfaf3f95cd163b629a05ecea4b7d1da02d","tid":2436702,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:46:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210307/557NYVXSDNG5TKJKJYKKKGYQGY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210307%2F557NYVXSDNG5TKJKJYKKKGYQGY%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bFm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=396bff5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210307%2F557NYVXSDNG5TKJKJYKKKGYQGY%2F&h=57779eaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210307/557NYVXSDNG5TKJKJYKKKGYQGY/</a><br />\n<br />\n自稱滿族紅三代「不想孩子活在控制下」<br />\n「中國天才」潛日 復出反共<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】曾被稱為「中國天才」的伊啟威（原名：吳迪釗）數年前突然銷聲匿迹，近月卻復出，還以「滿族」及「紅三代」的身份頻頻抨擊中共，背景頗為神秘。伊接受本報訪問，稱外祖父是中央警衞局的衞士，負責保衞毛澤東等國家領導人，但不願透露父親身份。現時他已入籍日本，只因「不希望自己下一代生活在中國控制的國家。」<br />\n<br />\n早在2010年，14歲的伊啟威出版長篇小說《救贖》，獲國務院學者推薦、中國文聯出版發行，在北京大學、深圳大學等地演講及舉辦發佈會，內地冠以「天才」，風頭一時無兩，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3j03qBtaTGfT9O11KWUl1kZDKQI=/1703x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AZ7R4H5LTBATPCRJ3ROYTCFKEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3j03qBtaTGfT9O11KWUl1kZDKQI%3D%2F1703x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAZ7R4H5LTBATPCRJ3ROYTCFKEM.jpg&h=86387b1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■自稱「紅三代」的伊啟威現已入籍日本。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外祖父曾負責護毛<br />\n<br />\n伊啟威透露自己是滿族人，外祖父在滿洲國長大，二戰後加入中共，1949年中共建政後，調入中央警衞局，負責保衞毛澤東等國家領導人。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n伊啟威形容自己少時已經渴望在中國從政，網上流傳一封「留美少年伊啟威致習大大的一封信」，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SpUlc8QIaRQlRZsTHgxuNn7TgAU=/948x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PSYMISRNNRATVJ22JP2LPQNEOE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSpUlc8QIaRQlRZsTHgxuNn7TgAU%3D%2F948x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPSYMISRNNRATVJ22JP2LPQNEOE.jpg&h=04e642ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■伊啟威與克林頓合照，贈送他創作的漫畫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HFG-Rdv7RPITVV54HhyluC57UU4=/886x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YJX5L2IZYRG6LPGNVJOCZD2PMQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHFG-Rdv7RPITVV54HhyluC57UU4%3D%2F886x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYJX5L2IZYRG6LPGNVJOCZD2PMQ.jpg&h=75247a06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■伊啟威自稱曾到中南海遊玩和拍照。受訪者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n父捲貪腐隨即逃離<br />\n<br />\n年少的他經歷如此風光，為何沒有扶搖直上，反失蹤數年？他解釋，因父親捲入貪腐醜聞。他透露父親曾擔任光大銀行某分行副行長、。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「過去幾年我不想與中國人再有任何關係，連普通話都不再說，除了出生地是中國之外，其他都與中國沒有關係。」。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sR6R7_W80ZmaS5Wu_w7VtDOy4Zo=/1824x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7FCXMWGTEZG7LAJHD5MGFWGSYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsR6R7_W80ZmaS5Wu_w7VtDOy4Zo%3D%2F1824x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7FCXMWGTEZG7LAJHD5MGFWGSYY.jpg&h=b9576e4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■伊啟威的外祖父年輕時曾任職中央警衞局。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OXNM6gQb36SILidADbnzkJK9LL4=/1016x1084/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QBIHHQPWT5ED3JXOOQKFZY3ZGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOXNM6gQb36SILidADbnzkJK9LL4%3D%2F1016x1084%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQBIHHQPWT5ED3JXOOQKFZY3ZGY.jpg&h=476146f1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}